      <lg xml:id="TVM1.2.3">
<l>nīrnuma teṉṟivai vērmutaṉ māyttiṟai</l>
<l>cērmi ṉuyirkkata ṉērniṟai yillē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>These called “you, yours”, destroy at the roots, the lord</l>
<l>join, for the soul there is no fullness like that.</l>
      </lg>
